item.title: Community College to Four-Year: Amanda Finn
item.description: Everyone’s academic journey is different. Just ask Amanda Finn- an undergraduate at Cal State University, Long Beach. Her passion and love for research is rooted in Kinesiology, and she aspires to be a professor one day. She is a friend from home who I wish I was closer with in high school. I hope y’all enjoy her journey as much as I did!
